---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
import quoteLogo from "../assets/business-govt-nz.png";
import jack from "../assets/newjack2.jpg";
import otis from "../assets/newotis.jpg";
import astroLogo from "../assets/AstroMediaLogo.svg";

import config from "~/data/config.json";
---

<div class="flex flex-col sm:mx-32">
  <Image
    src={astroLogo}
    alt={`${config.businessName} background image`}
    class="my-8 h-16 mx-auto"
  />
  <ContentSection title="What is Astro Media?" id="intro-section-1">
    <Fragment slot="lead">
      Astro Media was founded in early 2023 because we noticed the lack of
      quality websites in our neighbourhood. We discovered that many small
      businesses were still using old websites that were slow and often had
      confusing layouts. <br />
      <br />
      This led to Jack Gong, a Software Engineering student and Otis Wales, a Computer
      Science student to come together to make changes in this landscape.
      <br />
      <br />
      Our primary mission is to deliver the best websites, that are <span
        class="text-primary"
        >Fully Custom
      </span>, <span class="text-primary">Beautiful</span> and <span
        class="text-primary"
        >Affordable
      </span>
    </Fragment>
  </ContentSection>
  <div class="mt-32 flex flex-col items-center sm:mx-16 xl:mx-32">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-2 items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-4 max-md:grid-cols-1"
    >
      <Image
        src={jack}
        class="rounded-2xl bg-default w-full h-full object-cover"
        alt=" Picture of co-founder Jack Gong"
      />
      <Image
        src={otis}
        class="rounded-2xl bg-default w-full h-full object-cover"
        alt="Picture of co-founder Otis Wales"
      />
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 italic">
      Founders <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jack-gong/">Jack Gong</a> & <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/otiswales/">Otis Wales</a
      >
    </p>
  </div>

  <figure
    class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-flip p-8 text-center"
  >
    <blockquote class="mx-auto mb-4 max-w-2xl text-flip lg:mb-8">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">
        "No business, whether you're part-time, self-employed, a start-up or you
        have a large staff, can afford to be without a digital presence."
      </h3>
    </blockquote>
    <a
      href="https://www.business.govt.nz/getting-started/building-a-brand/getting-an-online-presence/"
    >
      <Image
        src={quoteLogo}
        class="w-40 rounded-2xl bg-default p-3 px-4"
        alt="business.govt.nz logo"
      />
    </a>
  </figure>
  <ContentSection title="" id="features">
    <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <h2
        class="gradient-text text-center font-extrabold tracking-tight text-6xl"
      >
        How we will help you grow
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-4xl text-center">
        We're not just web developers; we're a team dedicated to boosting your
        business through top-notch website design in {config.city}. Our
        custom-coded solutions are crafted to tackle your unique challenges
        head-on, without being boxed in by CMS limitations. Need a mobile app, a
        bespoke e-commerce application, or a slick new website? We've got you
        covered. Searching for the best website developers near me? Look no
        further - our expertise is right at your doorstep.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-16 grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 border-default bg-offset p-8"
          style="min-height: 300px;"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-primary p-3 text-primary"
          >
            <Icon name="mdi:code-braces-box" />
          </div>
          <h1 class="mb-4 text-center font-extrabold text-2xl">
            Custom Websites
          </h1>
          <p class="text-center">
            We craft tailor-made websites that are not only lightning-fast but
            look amazing. Expect to have a website that is unique to your brand
            and is fully customisable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 border-default bg-offset p-8"
          style="min-height: 300px;"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-primary p-3 text-primary"
          >
            <Icon name="mdi:search-web" />
          </div>
          <h1 class="mb-4 text-center font-extrabold text-2xl">Social Media</h1>
          <p class="text-center">
            We understand the power of social media in connecting with your
            audience and growing your brand. Looking to stand out in {
              config.city
            }? Let us analyse your social media activity and provide actionable
            insights to boost your presence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 border-default bg-offset p-8"
          style="min-height: 300px;"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-primary p-3 text-primary"
          >
            <Icon name="mdi:account" />
          </div>
          <h1 class="mb-4 text-center font-extrabold text-2xl">
            Constant Support
          </h1>
          <p class="text-center">
            If you're facing issues with your website, don't worry â€” we're here
            to help. By being in-person in {config.city}, we're more readily
            available to provide constant support and promptly address any
            concerns.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center sm:mx-32 md:mx-64"
    >
      <!-- <h1 class="mt-8 font-extrabold text-2xl">
        Interested in getting started with us?
      </h1>
      <a
        href="mailto:therunningbeta@gmail.com"
        class="mt-8 w-full rounded-md border border-black p-8 text-center font-bold text-primary transition duration-300 ease-in-out text-2xl hover:bg-black hover:text-white"
        role="button"
      >
        Email now
      </a> -->
    </div>
  </ContentSection>
  <!-- <ContentSection title="Pricing" id="pricing">
    <Fragment slot="lead">
      We do things a little differently. Instead of large upfront costs, we
      offer a straightforward monthly subscription of <br /><span
        class="text-primary">$50 NZD</span
      >. <br /><br />That includes hosting, unlimited edits, 24/7 support, help
      with your Google profile, the works.
    </Fragment>
  </ContentSection> -->
</div>
